sequenceDiagram
participant Developer
participant DIS as Deployment & Integration System (DIS)
participant CoreSystems as Core Systems (PMS/MMS)
participant Cloud

Developer->>Developer: Implement new feature in PMS/MMS
Developer->>DIS: Commit and push code
DIS->>DIS: Build Docker image
DIS->>DIS: Push container image
DIS->>DIS: Validate deployment
DIS->>CoreSystems: Deploy updated PMS/MMS services
CoreSystems-->>DIS: Deployment successful
DIS->>Cloud: Update cloud deployment
Cloud-->>DIS: Confirm updates
